Class WhereClause

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.harvard.hms.dbmi.bd2k.irct.model.query.ClauseAbstract
      • edu.harvard.hms.dbmi.bd2k.irct.model.query.WhereClause
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    @Entity
public class WhereClause
extends ClauseAbstract
implements java.io.Serializable
    The where clause contains information used in a query to filter upon the data. A where clause can be done on a single query, a subquery or path.
    Author:
    Jeremy R. Easton-Marks
